Summon Creature	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AbominationSubRaceTrait.SpecialQuality.SpellLike	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Abominations can summon creatures associated either with the portfolio of their godly progenitor or with their imprisonment. For example, an abomination whose deific father's portfolio included the sky might be able to summon air elementals, while another abomination sealed away deep in the earth might be able to summon earth elementals (regardless of its mother's or father's portfolio). Summoned creatures serve the abomination without question. Summoned creatures automatically return whence they came after 1 hour, or sooner if slain. See specific abomination entries for additional details on summoning.	KEY:Abomination ~ Summon Creature																											SOURCEPAGE:ELH
