Amorphous Physiology	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:NehThalgguRaceTrait.SpecialQuality.Extraordinay	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A brain collector does not have fixed organs as do life forms from our reality. As such, it is immune to critical hits, death from massive damage, sneak attacks, and coup de grace.	KEY:Neh-Thalggu ~ Amorphous Physiology																		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Immunity to Critical Hits|Immunity To Death from Massive Damage|Immunity to Sneak Attack|Immunity To Coup de Grace									SOURCEPAGE:ELH
